Take a spectacular journey back through time and trace the transformation of a perfect angel into Satan, the arch demon. Witness the creation of a beautiful new world and feel the suspense as the devil brings his rebellion to Planet Earth. Behold the tremendous sacrifice of Christ.If you['ve ever wondered "why do bad things happen to good people?" This film is for you.
